-- Italy to Realign Renewable Energy Incentives With EU Levels
-- B y   C h i a r a   V a s a r r i
-- 2012-04-11T16:50:57Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-11/italy-to-realign-renewable-energy-incentives-with-eu-levels.html
Italy will bring its renewable
energy incentives into line with European Union levels and with
current market prices, the Industry Ministry said.  “The new regime lays the groundwork for an orderly and
sustainable development for renewable energy,” the Rome-based
ministry said in an e-mailed statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
